/c>t<lb/>herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>mit den allerbe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Grüßen an Deine liebe <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs><lb/>Dein<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed></closer></div></body></text></TEI>